{
  "texts": [
    "We conduct chain of thought (CoT) prompting [43].",
    "This few-shot approach involves providing LLMs with question and stepby-step reasoning answer examples.",
    "In addition, we include results obtained from GPT-4 and HuggingChat (which uses LLaMA-1) as well.",
    "We chose HuggingChat due to its popularity and ease of use.",
    "The corresponding prompts are reported in S2.The results are illustrated in Fig. 1."
  ]
}